data.description: Indulge in the charm, updates, and potential this beautiful home has to offer.  Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the custom hall tree and the tastefully updated fixtures, setting a warm and inviting tone for this meticulously maintained home. The interior boasts new carpeting in all three bedrooms, updated flooring, and a fresh coat of paint throughout most of the home, creating an ambiance of comfort and style. The open floor plan provides a versatile layout that is perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying your day-to-day routines. In the back yard you will find a serene retreat featuring a covered patio and pergola, making it an ideal spot for relaxation and entertaining. This outdoor haven complements the indoor charm, offering a seamless extension of your living space. This beautiful home not only offers a comfortable and stylish living space but also provides endless potential for you to create the lifestyle you desire. Beyond the property lines, the neighborhood adds even more appeal. Residents have access to a playground, a walking trail, and a fishing pond, enhancing the sense of community and providing recreational opportunities for all ages. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home. Listing Agent is related to seller.
